316
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:19,590
Tang San.

317
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:24,680
Why didn't you come in?

318
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:28,430
Mr. Su.

319
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,280
I thought about it all night long.

320
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,430
My dad, the village head,

321
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:33,070
and you

322
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:33,710
told me

323
00:24:33,710 --> 00:24:34,800
about the World of Martial Soul

324
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:35,560
beyond the Saint of Soul Village.

325
00:24:36,190 --> 00:24:37,430
But each one of you

326
00:24:37,430 --> 00:24:38,350
told a different story.

327
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:40,560
Since you are eager to know,

328
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:42,280
you should figure it out yourself.

329
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,520
Don't you want to know

330
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,880
what your own Martial Soul

331
00:24:46,950 --> 00:24:48,640
or your family's Martial Soul is?

332
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,680
I can also know
my family's Martial Soul?

333
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,710
Martial Soul can be inherited in the family.

334
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:56,830
The Martial Soul of either parent

335
00:24:56,830 --> 00:24:57,920
will go to their offspring.

336
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,880
You didn't cower when you
confronted the Human Faced Demon Spider.

337
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:05,920
I can see that you are

338
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:06,880
strong-hearted.

339
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,070
I believe that your Martial Soul

340
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,520
may also be powerful and special.

341
00:25:13,710 --> 00:25:15,640
So you are very likely to have

342
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:16,880
the potential of becoming a Soul Master.

343
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,160
Apart from becoming a Soul Master,

344
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:20,070
is there any other way to get stronger?

345
00:25:22,470 --> 00:25:23,640
In Douluo Continent,

346
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,800
there are no other possibilities.

347
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:32,230
I want to get stronger.
I want to be a Soul Master.

348
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:38,760
Stretch out your right hand.

349
00:25:55,800 --> 00:25:57,000
Blue Silver Plant?

350
00:25:58,230 --> 00:26:00,280
How could it be Blue Silver Plant?

351
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:16,400
Come out.

352
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:20,070
Is this my Martial Soul?

353
00:26:22,800 --> 00:26:23,280
This...

354
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,070
Blue Silver Plant

355
00:26:26,280 --> 00:26:27,830
is the commonest useless Martial Soul.

356
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:30,520
It can neither attack, defend,

357
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,520
nor support.

358
00:26:32,230 --> 00:26:34,070
A person with such a useless Martial Soul

359
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,830
can never be a Soul Master.

360
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:39,680
I can't get stronger anymore?

361
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:41,190
Since you are here,

362
00:26:41,190 --> 00:26:42,190
take the test

363
00:26:42,190 --> 00:26:43,310
and see how strong your Soul Power is.

364
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:46,430
