379
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:34,760
Do you want to join

380
00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:36,950
Nuoding School?

381
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,470
Don't I have a useless Martial Soul?

382
00:27:43,070 --> 00:27:43,680
Why didn't you

383
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:44,920
go with Su Yun Tao?

384
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,800
