385
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:50,280
I forbid you to go
to the awakening rite,

386
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:51,800
but you went there anyway.

387
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:55,230
Dad, I know I was wrong.

388
00:27:55,560 --> 00:27:56,800
But Mr. Su said

389
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,590
I inherited my Martial Soul

390
00:27:57,590 --> 00:27:58,950
from you and my mom.

391
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:01,160
I joined the Martial Soul Awakening Rite

392
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,760
in order to know more

393
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:03,880
about my mom.

394
00:28:06,830 --> 00:28:08,070
What is your Martial Soul?

395
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,470
They told me

396
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:20,110
it is a useless Martial Soul,

397
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:22,190
but I still stand a chance.

398
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,640
I can become a Soul Master

399
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:26,110
and attend Soul Master School.

400
00:28:26,710 --> 00:28:28,760
You chose this path in the end.

401
00:28:35,230 --> 00:28:36,040
I allow you to go,

402
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:37,760
on two conditions.

403
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:42,520
You can be a Soul Master,

404
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:45,190
but you must not join Martial Soul Hall.

405
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,430
Why?

406
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:49,310
Make a vow.

407
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,230
I vow

408
00:28:51,470 --> 00:28:52,640
that even if I become a Soul Master,

409
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:54,470
I will never join Martial Soul Hall.

410
00:28:57,710 --> 00:28:58,350
But Dad,

411
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,070
as they said, I've got a useless Martial Soul.

412
00:29:11,230 --> 00:29:12,070
Make the fire stronger.

413
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,470
Aren't you curious

414
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,160
about Xuan Yu Hand's function?

415
00:29:16,760 --> 00:29:17,920
I will tell you now.

416
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:25,800
Make the fire stronger.

417
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,830
Dad, does the Martial Soul

418
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:30,430
only manifest on the right hand?

419
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:33,800
I somehow felt that there was

420
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:35,760
something hidden in my left hand

421
00:29:35,760 --> 00:29:37,070
when I was
at the Martial Soul Awakening Rite.

422
00:29:40,830 --> 00:29:41,590
Spread your palm.

423
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,280
Focus.

424
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,400
Release the power in your heart.

425
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:00,800
Twin Martial Souls?

426
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:03,590
Is having Twin Martial Souls rare?

427
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,190
Make it visible.

428
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:10,400
Dad.

429
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:11,470
This is so difficult.

430
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:13,070
I feel that something in my heart

431
00:30:13,070 --> 00:30:14,470
is suppressing me.

432
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,040
Release your inner strength.

433
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,070
It really is Hao Tian Hammer.

434
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,830
Hao Tian Hammer?

435
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:35,400
Dad.

436
00:30:35,710 --> 00:30:38,110
This hammer looks ugly.

437
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:39,920
It's too heavy.

438
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,680
Dad, I can't hold on anymore.

439
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:43,590
Take it back.

440
00:30:49,950 --> 00:30:50,920
Don't let anyone see

441
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:52,520
