444
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:57,590
If one day,

445
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:01,830
this hammer can no longer be restrained,

446
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,000
you must remember

447
00:31:03,430 --> 00:31:05,470
that this hammer is not a tool for killing.

448
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:07,110
It is meant to be a guardian.

449
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:10,110
A guardian?

450
00:31:10,430 --> 00:31:11,230
What does it guard?

451
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,590
It guards your right hand

452
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:15,640
and protects the Blue Silver Plant
in your right hand.

453
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,000
Remember.

454
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:19,920
In the future,

455
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:21,800
always protect the plant
in your right hand

456
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:23,430
with the hammer in your left hand.

457
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:24,640
Always.

458
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,280
I remember it, Dad.

459
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:31,830
Look.

460
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:41,800
This is the second condition.

461
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:43,350
You have to work this piece of iron

462
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:44,470
