463
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:46,520
Then, you can leave.

464
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:48,520
Dad.

465
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:51,070
Are you exaggerating it?

466
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:54,190
Look at me.

467
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:15,040
It is too fast to be seen.

468
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:17,000
Use Purple Demon Eye.

469
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:28,470
I see it clearly.

470
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:29,880
The hammer

471
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:31,160
