472
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,160
It makes no mistake.

473
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:35,710
This is the gist of Tempering a Thousandfold.

474
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,800
Gather all your strength at one point.

475
00:32:38,230 --> 00:32:39,560
Turn a piece of ordinary metal
into a magic weapon.

476
00:32:40,800 --> 00:32:41,710
This is Xuan Yu Hand.

477
00:32:42,590 --> 00:32:43,230
When you use the hammer,

478
00:32:43,560 --> 00:32:45,110
